{"tid":1800302,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)壯志凌雲 魅影殺機","createTime":"2019-12-27T16:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T19:28:42.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f22f6330d5f7fd227538254b4cad560fe126f220","tid":1800302,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=bbb2e17d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=2d8dace4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OKRU 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=40b6b779\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/1d/Top_Gun_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F1d%2FTop_Gun_poster.jpg&h=23f671dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.《捍衛戰士》描述一位原本自信滿滿而年輕的F-14戰機海軍飛行員彼得&middot;「小孤牛」&middot;米契爾上尉（LT Pete &quot;Maverick&quot; Mitchell，湯姆&middot;克魯斯 飾），<br />\n因為優秀的飛行技術與機緣，獲選加入美國海軍最頂尖的飛行訓練單位&mdash;&mdash;美國海軍戰鬥武器學校&mdash;&mdash;接受訓練。在飛行學校中米契爾遇到在該校擔任教官的夏綠蒂&middot;「恰莉」&middot;布萊克伍德（Charlotte 'Charlie' Blackwood，凱莉&middot;麥吉莉絲 飾）並發展出戀情<br />\n<br />\n2.1992年，哥倫比亞九歲女孩卡塔莉亞（柔伊&middot;莎達娜飾），其父母因握有毒梟唐路易的不法跡証，被唐路易派人殺害。父母雙亡的卡塔莉亞刺傷了唐路易部下的馬可，透過中央情報局的幫助，從波哥大逃到美國，卡塔莉亞認為中情局不可靠，隻身來到了芝加哥，投奔叔叔艾米利歐<br />\n<br />\n12 40AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=5e63ac71\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=e85ad6cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ac46875ca6c72ba5d7bad45fda778b38ab912d","tid":1800302,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bc/Colombiana.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbc%2FColombiana.jpg&h=5403174a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aef6b5010a799e915871debc8e72afbdf0094569","tid":1800302,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"（聯署）你班友快Ｄ同我簽晒佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih